column5: Hey OFC!  Put together a slideshow of pictures and a few video clips from 2010. All fish are from the Soo area!  Just a heads up, its a bit long! 10 mins....    TDunns fishing with family and friends   TDunn
Great season. The atlantics look awesome. Good luck in 2011!
An excellent recap Tyler. Some super fish in there too! Thanks for sharing.
Awesome    That's some solid recap You certainly no slouch   Congrats TDunn Thanks for taking the time!!! Leechman
Great recap Tyler.  Some awesome fish, pics and vids you got.  Cool tunes too!
Thanks guys! I love to read reports/reviews on the board. You can actually learn a lot from them. I must admit, I enjoy posting them also!   TDunn
Very nice Tyler, and sure would like a crack at those Atlantics if I can ever get up there at the right time.
Cool vid Tyler, you sure have some great fishing at your doorstep.
Awesome budday!  You're making me rethink my choice of ear candy for the next montage.  Did you get that second batch of leaders?
Very cool mate! Great song too
